### Crear una nueva mascota (SIN token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Firulais",
  "birth_date": "2021-05-10",
  "type": "Perro",
  "color": "Marrón",
  "owner_id": 10,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar una mascota (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/public/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Firulais Actualizado",
  "birth_date": "2021-05-10",
  "type": "Perro",
  "color": "Negro",
  "owner_id": 1,
