### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todas las mascotas (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener mascota por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear una nueva mascota (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Michi",
  "birth_date": "2022-01-15",
  "type": "Gato",
  "color": "Blanco",
  "owner_id": 2,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar una mascota (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
